thread.title_full: BRIEF-Altor sells 4 pct of shares in Dustin to institutional investors | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Altor sells 4 pct of shares in Dustin to institutional investors
text:
Oct 16 Altor Fund II:
* Altor Fund II (Altor) has today sold 3,000,000 shares, representing 4 pct of share capital and votes, in Dustin Group AB to a limited number of institutional investors
Source text: bit.ly/1LnVvVb
Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
